# ==============================================================================
# CHAPTER 2  —  The POST workaround
# ==============================================================================

### 2) Same 1,000 SKUs, but now the list lives in a JSON body. No length
###    problem — but we've lied about semantics:
###      - POST is unsafe + non-idempotent (RFC 9110).
###      - Shared caches WILL NOT cache POST responses.
###      - Retry libraries (Polly, browser fetch) won't auto-retry POST.
POST {{host}}/api/v2/products/prices
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

