# CHAPTER 3  —  The QUERY method (RFC 10008)
# ==============================================================================

### 3) Same body as request 2. Only the verb changed. RFC 10008 declares
###    QUERY BOTH safe AND idempotent, which means:
###      - Response is cacheable (Cache-Control header comes back).
###      - Retries are safe.
###      - Semantics match reality: this is a READ, not a mutation.
QUERY {{host}}/api/v3/products/prices
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

